{"id":267022,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-上海千名维权者到市政府抗议腐败，警方/","date":"2012-12-06T11:15:53Z","modified":"2012-12-06T11:15:53Z","title":"维权网 | 上海千名维权者到市政府抗议腐败，警方一度喷辣椒水驱赶（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员雷鸣报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>星期三，是上海维权者向市委市人大市政府抗议的日子。上午八时，维权者陆续从上海各区县聚集到位于上海市人民大道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>号的市委、市政府、人大市信访办，抗议当局掠夺公民合法的私有房屋、宅基地、自留地、承包地等财产，抗议司法不公、枉法判决，抗议医疗事故讨不到一个说法，抗议迫害反腐败维权人士，将依法维权者关进黑监狱、行政拘留、刑事拘留、逮捕、劳教、送精神病院等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>时左右，市委市人大市政府信访办门前已聚集了一千多位抗议者，遭到警察（约五十人）驱赶。突然，人群中响起凄惨的呼救声。原来，是一名警察偷偷向人群喷射辣椒水，还强行将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>名抗议者暴打后拖上警车抓走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>十八大刚刚结束，国际大都市的上海发生如此一幕，人们抱着对依法治国、改善民生的希望也再次落空。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家都已经明白：只有铲除腐败根源，社会才能和谐稳定。腐败不铲除，老百姓的权利就永远得不到维护。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>有抗议者高举国民党国父 孙中山 先生的画像，表示对 孙中山 先生的怀念，对 孙中山 先生创建的国民党的敬仰和爱戴。回想当年国民党在大陆执政时，没有发生抢了老百姓的房屋土地还要把人行政拘留、刑事拘留、逮捕、判刑、劳教、关黑监狱、送精神病院等恶劣事件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>抗议者高呼“国民党万岁”、“奥巴马千岁”、“腐败伤民心”、“打倒腐败”、“独裁专制误国殃民不得人心”等口号的声音在上海市委市政府上空回荡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>时左右，抗议者全部离开，各自回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-MXZcPr0YFPM/UMBv2mLUYvI/AAAAAAAAVO4/LuY9-tMGSuc/s1600/20121205A007.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-MXZcPr0YFPM/UMBv2mLUYvI/AAAAAAAAVO4/LuY9-tMGSuc/s1600/20121205A007.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-M_X52CC00qo/UMBv4UzOZ8I/AAAAAAAAVPA/GUqk2Ne05A8/s1600/20121205A008.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-M_X52CC00qo/UMBv4UzOZ8I/AAAAAAAAVPA/GUqk2Ne05A8/s1600/20121205A008.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-BTt2MyY0wQ0/UMBv5QezFaI/AAAAAAAAVPE/42m-V3KUCXA/s1600/20121205A014.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-BTt2MyY0wQ0/UMBv5QezFaI/AAAAAAAAVPE/42m-V3KUCXA/s1600/20121205A014.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ttDsynpXpcA/UMBv7E-O3SI/AAAAAAAAVPQ/qXaap4g9tBA/s1600/20121205A015.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ttDsynpXpcA/UMBv7E-O3SI/AAAAAAAAVPQ/qXaap4g9tBA/s1600/20121205A015.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-QgfTpai2AcQ/UMBv8d9DPzI/AAAAAAAAVPY/L_UeDi-ChVc/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-QgfTpai2AcQ/UMBv8d9DPzI/AAAAAAAAVPY/L_UeDi-ChVc/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></b></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-266156850268028943?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}